---
// The "peace, not war" moment. Soft, warm, calm.
// Sits between sections — no number, no header — just a breath.
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 relative overflow-hidden">
  {/* Ambient soft orbs */}
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="soft-orb animate-float-slow" style="width: 420px; height: 420px; top: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(247, 212, 192, 0.6), transparent 60%);"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 relative text-center">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 chip mb-8">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <circle cx="8" cy="8" r="6.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" />
        <path d="M 8 1.5 V 14.5 M 8 8 L 13 5 M 8 8 L 13 11" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
      </svg>
      The stance
    </div>

    <h2 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-[1.02] tracking-tight mb-6">
      We're here to make <span class="italic text-padkos">peace,</span><br />
      not to make war.
    </h2>

    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-ink-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
      Macrosofty isn't a protest. It's an alternative. We're not here to convert anyone, shame anyone, or fight anyone. If your current setup works for you — cool, enjoy.
    </p>

    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-lg text-ink-700 leading-relaxed mb-10">
      If it stopped working, or stopped respecting you, there's a door open over here. Walk through when you're ready. No sales pitch.
    </p>

    <p class="font-display text-xl italic text-ink-900">
      "Free for everyone. Forever."
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500">
      Lekker at a braai · not locked at a boardroom
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
